# Global Rules

- Don't over-engineer — no abstractions, helpers, or patterns beyond what's asked
- When removing something, delete it fully — no stubs, no commented-out code
- Styling and positioning live in the component file, not the parent
- Add a short inline comment only where a value needs to be tweaked (e.g. `// ← adjust bottom spacing`)
- Don't change size or rotation unless explicitly asked
- Prefer editing existing files over creating new ones
- Keep responses short and direct
